{"tid":360681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個街 成ocamp mk友係到玩排擠","createTime":"2017-08-15T13:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T04:33:48.000Z","uid":54581,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76200ebcf12974b6a1bf66d351c5725f95c78efa","tid":360681,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾<br />\n<br />\n我本身諗住入ocamp食組媽，點撚知俾v組巴當狗咁撚<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母，玩親密game就偏我同條毒撚一對咁玩<br />\n人地毛毛蟲就梅花間竹咁，條仔對腳又磨落前邊條女既大脾，隻手就扶撚知後邊隻靚腳，間唔中又挨後食波餅 睇到我扯晒旗<br />\n<br />\n到我玩就前後都係仔，仲要得4條友一隊，又撚鳩我地話個場唔夠大，要最尾solo咁玩，個個都玩晒就睇住我地4條仔on99咁un下un下，屌佢老母西。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩撚完mass game係水戰，要單腳跳鬥撞battle, 人地mk仔借啲意扶住條女，批下對奶咁<br />\n<br />\n到我又係最尾玩，仲要同個肥妹仔1on1, 最黎俾佢撞撚到扒落地下，佢又失平衡壓鳩住我，胸骨都差啲斷，小腳又瘀晒 仲要聽到成班友連埋組媽組女笑到仆街<br />\n<br />\n最後無人扶我，成班去左玩濕身淫亂game<br />\n我就un下un下咁行去場邊睇住成班木咀獸父係到飛擒大咬；<br />\n<br />\n後尾發現大脾流緊血，應該俾人推低個陣擦親，自己行15分鐘去醫療室到止血。<br />\n<br />\n跟住我覺得好番7788，行到又唔流血，諗住可以係水球大戰到掉鳩囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻膠布都唔撚痴狗沖番去個場。<br />\n<br />\n點鳩知去到人影都無，我當堂灰晒機，坐係場邊半粒鐘先有人搵我<br />\n一望見係組媽打俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，諗住佢地應該搞緊驚喜俾我（因我就生日，報名有寫生日日期）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知一聽佢話唔知我去左邊，所以成班人就出去玩city hunt, 叫我自己參觀下大學先。。<br />\n<br />\n我真係屌佢老母，原來我俾左成千蚊係黎遊花園，仲要俾人玩 真係好撚嬲，最後玩房game我決定報復，佢地玩乜柒都唔理，係張床坐係到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51afe1ed9f26350c6d68d9324a60ac9556fe23f6","tid":360681,"uid":64178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"今日都係 <br />\n毒撚真係唔好去ocamp"},{"pid":"6e69a3480246b41093e0a370f2a59b398d2fec94","tid":360681,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e7cac6ed60c5c38c81e82d18696fb60e3502b5","tid":360681,"uid":76399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪成隻狗咁流哂口水望住啲女呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7113803ebd68d6a80913b3ce1402052db6e8874","tid":360681,"uid":126952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"呢啲算咩報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地本身都唔想預你一齊玩 依家叫都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b577d59544e9683870c00515434fb6a7608748d","tid":360681,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪成隻狗咁流哂口水望住啲女呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個鳩個都係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n見我靚仔就玩鳩我"},{"pid":"9da9bd27549c21c10c2e8113282de6a154392b34","tid":360681,"uid":77136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲算咩報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地本身都唔想預你一齊玩 依家叫都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬訓左都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00b4382e8a814a3e53aea57065836847eeb4424","tid":360681,"uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲算咩報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地本身都唔想預你一齊玩 依家叫都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下，我望到班友頹晒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5128407764727a4eced0cb8f730c22ade5509f7a","tid":360681,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"今次無是咁的<br />\n零分"},{"pid":"5344f4fabff05196870648550d02d65b2c927f10","tid":3606